sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:entrezGene:
Gnaq
(a.k.a. 1110005L02Rik, 6230401I02Rik, AA408290, AW060788, Dsk1, Dsk10, Galphaq, Gq, GqI)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:mutation: BamHI and SacI sites in alpha-q were removed with silent mutations. EYFP contains substitution of His for Asn164.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:tagsFusionProteins: CFP was inserted internally into the alpha-q sequence between residues 124 and 125 with a SGGGGS linker on each end of the YFP. The EE epitope was introduced into the alpha-q sequence by mutating residues 171-176 (SYLPTQ) to EYMPTE.
